<c74object name='sp.boppad' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Interface for the KMI BopPad
</digest>
    <description>Interface for the KMI BopPad.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.boppad</o> object acts as a parser for the Keith McMillen BopPad. It outputs note/velocity pairs, XY coordinites in a grid-ified space, and pressure/aftertouch.
</discussion>

	<metadatalist>
		<metadata name='author'>Rodrigo Constanzo, Flucoma Project</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Machine Learning</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Audio Analysis</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Onset Detection</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Corpus Playback</metadata>
	</metadatalist>

